results.full_model_response:

2) Move all terms to one side: 98 - 94*d² = 0
3) Subtract 98 from both sides: -94*d² = -98
4) Divide both sides by -94: d² = 98/94
5) Take the square root of both sides: d = ±√(98/94)
6) Calculate 98/94 ≈ 1.0425531915...
7) Take square root: √1.0425531915... ≈ 1.0210
8) Therefore d = ±1.0210

<answer>-1.0210, 1.0210</answer>
